Provides: pipewire
Conflicts: pipewire, pulseaudio
Replaces: pipewire
Description: HiFiBerry PipeWire multimedia server
 PipeWire is a server and user space API to deal with multimedia pipelines.
 This includes:
 .
  - Making available sources of video (such as from a capture devices or
    application provided streams) and multiplexing this with clients.
  - Accessing sources of audio and video for consumption.
  - Generating graphs for audio and video processing.
 .
 This custom package is optimized for HiFiBerry devices with system-wide
 configuration and includes WirePlumber session manager.
